sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Web/Mobile)
    participant W as Web Services (Spring Boot)
    participant CAT as Catalog Service
    participant INV as Inventory Service
    participant CART as Cart Service

    C->>W: GET /products
    W->>CAT: GET /products
    CAT-->>W: Product list
    W-->>C: Product list (JSON)

    C->>W: POST /carts/{cartId}/items
    W->>CART: POST /carts/{cartId}/items
    CART->>INV: GET /inventory/{productId}
    INV-->>CART: availableQuantity
    CART->>CAT: GET /products/{productId}
    CAT-->>CART: Product details (price, name)
    CART-->>W: Updated Cart
    W-->>C: Updated Cart (totals, items)
